DESCRIPTION:Join best friends and rising comedy stars Abi Sharp and Harsh f
 or a split bill that explores the intersection of Type-A ambition\, queer i
 dentity\, and the chaotic search for love. United by their nerdy neuroses a
 nd a spectacular track record of romantic failures\, the pair present A Mar
 riage of Inconvenience: a show about the logistical nightmare of modern dat
 ing\, and their pact to enter a sexless lavender marriage if they're still 
 single by 40. Until then\, they're saying "I do" to the next best thing: aw
 kwardly sharing the stage for half an hour each.\nMore info: https://comedy
 atlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/a-marriage-of-inconvenience/
